Commercial Quote Business Process

We've created a quote business process for General Liability. You can create and modify quotes directly on the Quote UI.

To create a quote, go to the Opportunities page and choose the Opportunity you're creating the quote for. Ensure that the Opportunity has a pricebook assigned.

Click into the Pricebook field and select Standard Pricebook. Enter quote details, select a plan, and click Next. Add building or business details as needed and configure coverages. Click Rate Now to use the rating procedure defined for General Liability.

Commercial Quote OmniScript powers commercial quoting using Rating Procedures and Integration Procedures. Create a Commercial Auto Quote Using OmniScript by adding details to create a quote for multiple vehicles associated with multiple locations.
